        rdfs:comment      "Rationale: Fig.4: TrkC and PTPσ Ectodomains Induce Excitatory Presynaptic and Postsynaptic Differentiation, Respectively. Experimental description: 7/11/2017 Pim\n- Species of cultured neurons is not explicitly stated in the paper.\n\nAwait species information (amcraig@interchange.ubc.ca , dd 7/11/2017)\n\n8/11/2017 Pim\n- Authors responded:\n\nRe. neuronal cultures, we used rat primary hippocampal neuron cultures.\n\n- The authors use rat neurons." ;
